    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2 键盘 ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            287,
            240,
            305
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "i 不同机型，键盘按键不同，请以实际为准。",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            326,
            460,
            342
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.1 快捷键功能介绍",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            147,
            362,
            337,
            378
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "计算机键盘的 F1、F2 等键默认为快捷键（热键）模式，可用于轻松执行常见任务。",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            400,
            798,
            418
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "table",
        "img_path": "images/b8f82385435cc8e687c7ffcd9aa654c56848f85eca814c0ea807c869ad8d8d57.jpg",
        "table_caption": [],
        "table_footnote": [],
        "table_body": "<table><tr><td><img src=\"images/f066d291502722b113e5788ae148c8a42eeffc08c94600fdae6679a4f5f6c687.jpg\"/></td><td>降低屏幕亮度</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/4ffc165639287d01582bd868c56a33e94773d9bc71a8b21bc546b315588a0a89.jpg\"/></td><td>增强屏幕亮度</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/b5bbb0ea9c4c1448088f06a565cbb85d62cea7d2cc75b29decf83df433656e3c.jpg\"/></td><td>开启或关闭键盘背光,调节键盘背光亮度i 如果此按键上无 业 图标,则不支持背光。</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/eba0c4655cc89ed6fb65514657094302faf339d926fba242ba67f8bc1e5abdcd.jpg\"/></td><td>开启或关闭静音</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/f3f88b4985d514ae0b1db794665c0e5cbeb63bc9779420820943a411496b52dd.jpg\"/></td><td>减小音量</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/12cb316af3f3738587764e832f07b81c732380058a0764313ba2a3cdc6c12558.jpg\"/></td><td>增大音量</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/06129412dd9c3597593ac1f41668990ab46e0862cf79e8b96bd46d544498d67e.jpg\"/></td><td>开启或关闭麦克风</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/66c6eb8452a2c934e6ff7eeed13b8eb91e6934804035ed4a9ffceb9a54f99b26.jpg\"/></td><td>切换投影屏幕模式</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/00f2df830da75a540b227d3d63d1ed5679665cfaf9214bc8c629b29ad964429d.jpg\"/></td><td>开启或关闭无线网络</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/f59f9fde72d66459661517ca446307a8697351e5b7e44058e1f909c048173e4b.jpg\"/></td><td>开启系统设置</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/95103eea64d30fe862225121d7d7a992cbacd16a273593d91824ca66e71033df.jpg\"/></td><td>截屏</td></tr><tr><td><img src=\"images/8f865fb12e6539de9b756ef3242ee49afb97444e3f3d994e5bad4833af4c74ff.jpg\"/></td><td>插入覆盖</td></tr></table>",
        "bbox": [
